$PROBLEM    2 compartment fitting
$INPUT       ID TIME AMT RATE DV MDV EVID WT AGE SEX BUN SCR OCC CRCL COV1 COV2

$DATA      /home/CertaraUser/Desktop/FDA-OGD-ML/examples/user/Example5/dataWithPeriod.csv IGNORE=@

$SUBROUTINE ADVAN4 ;; advan4
$PK
  CWTKGONE = WT/81  ;; WEIGHT CENTERED ON ONE
  CWTKGZERO = WT-81 ;; WEIGHT CENTERED ON ZERO
  CAGE = AGE/60     ;; AGE CENTERED ON ONE
  CCRCL = CRCL/85.6 ;; CRCL CENTERD ON ONE
  CCOV1 = COV1-15.4 ;; COVARIATE 1 CENTERED ON ZERO
  IOVV = 0
  TVV2=THETA(1)   *CAGE**THETA(7)   *EXP(IOVV)
  V2=TVV2*EXP(ETA(2))
  IOVCL = 0
  TVCL= THETA(3) *CWTKGONE**THETA(8)  *CCRCL**THETA(9)  *EXP(IOVCL)
  CL=TVCL*EXP(ETA(1))

  K=CL/V2
  K23=THETA(4)*CWTKGONE**THETA(6)
  K32=THETA(5)*CWTKGONE**THETA(6)
  D1=THETA(10) *EXP(ETA(4)) ; infusion only
  TVKA=THETA(2)
  KA=TVKA  *EXP(ETA(3)) 
  S2 = V2
$ERROR
  REP = IREP
  IPRED =F
  IOBS = F +EPS(1)
  Y=IOBS
$THETA
  (0.001,100) 	; THETA(1) V  UNITS = L
  (0.001, 10) 	; THETA(2) KA UNITS = 1/HR
  (0.001,2)	; THETA(3) CL UNITS =  L/HR
  (0.001,0.02)  	 ; THETA(4) K23 
  (0.001,0.3) 	 ; THETA(5) K32 
  (0,0.1) 	; THETA(6) K23~WT 	 ; init for K23~WT 


  (-4,0.8) 	; THETA(7) POWER volume ~AGE 

  (-4,.7) 	; THETA(8) POWER clearance~WT 

  (-4,-0.2) 	; THETA(9) POWER clearance~CRCL 

  (0.01,0.2) 		;; THETA(10) D1  
$OMEGA
  0.1  		; ETA(1) CLEARANCE
  0.4  		; ETA(2) VOLUME
$OMEGA ;; 2nd OMEGA block 
  0.1		; ETA(3) ETA ON KA
$OMEGA BLOCK(2) ;; block OMEGA block 
  0.1 		;; ETA(4) ETA ON ALAG1
  0.01 0.1 		;; ETA(5) ETA ON D1  
  ;; no iov ON CL
  ;; no iov ON V
$SIGMA
  200 	; EPS(1) additive error

$EST METHOD=COND INTER MAX = 9999 MSFO=MSF1 PRINT = 10
$COV UNCOND PRINT=E  PRECOND=1 PRECONDS=TOS  MATRIX = R

  0.4  		; ETA(2) VOLUME

$SUBROUTINE ADVAN4 ;; advan4
$PK
  CWTKGONE = WT/81  ;; WEIGHT CENTERED ON ONE
  CWTKGZERO = WT-81 ;; WEIGHT CENTERED ON ZERO
  CAGE = AGE/60     ;; AGE CENTERED ON ONE
  CCRCL = CRCL/85.6 ;; CRCL CENTERD ON ONE
  CCOV1 = COV1-15.4 ;; COVARIATE 1 CENTERED ON ZERO
  IF(OCC.EQ.1) IOVV = ETA(6) 
  IF(OCC.EQ.2) IOVV = ETA(7) 
  IF(OCC.EQ.3) IOVV = ETA(8)
  TVV2=THETA(1)  *EXP(SEX*THETA(7)) *CAGE**THETA(8) *EXP(COV2*THETA(9))  *EXP(IOVV)
  V2=TVV2*EXP(ETA(2))
  IOVCL = 0
  TVCL= THETA(3) *CWTKGONE**THETA(10)  *CCRCL**THETA(11)  *EXP(IOVCL)
  CL=TVCL*EXP(ETA(1))

  K=CL/V2
  K23=THETA(4)*CWTKGONE**THETA(6)
  K32=THETA(5)*CWTKGONE**THETA(6)
  ALAG1=THETA(12)*EXP(ETA(4))
  ;; No D1
  TVKA=THETA(2)
  KA=TVKA  *EXP(ETA(3)) 
  S2 = V2
$ERROR
  REP = IREP
  IPRED =F
  IOBS = F *EXP(EPS(1))+EPS(2)
  Y=IOBS
$THETA
  (0.001,100) 	; THETA(1) V  UNITS = L
  (0.001, 10) 	; THETA(2) KA UNITS = 1/HR
  (0.001,20)	; THETA(3) CL UNITS =  L/HR
  (0.001,0.02)  	 ; THETA(4) K23 
  (0.001,0.3) 	 ; THETA(5) K32 
  (0,0.1) 	; THETA(6) K23~WT 	 ; init for K23~WT 

  (-4,0.1) 	; THETA(7) EXPONENTIAL volume~SEX 
  (-4,0.8) 	; THETA(8) POWER volume ~AGE 
  (-4,0.1) 	; THETA(9) EXPONENTIAL volume ~COV2 
  (-4,.7) 	; THETA(10) POWER clearance~WT 

  (-4,-0.2) 	; THETA(11) POWER clearance~CRCL 

  (0.001,0.1) 	; THETA(12) ALAG1   
$OMEGA
  0.1  		; ETA(1) CLEARANCE
  0.4  		; ETA(2) VOLUME
$OMEGA ;; 2nd OMEGA block 
  0.1		; ETA(3) ETA ON KA
$OMEGA BLOCK(2) ;; block OMEGA block 
  0.1 		;; ETA(4) ETA ON ALAG1
  0.01 0.1 		;; ETA(5) ETA ON D1
  ;; no iov ON CL
$OMEGA BLOCK(1) ; ETA(6)
  0.1 
$OMEGA BLOCK SAME ; ETA(7)
$OMEGA BLOCK SAME ; ETA(8)
$SIGMA
  0.1 	; EPS(1) proportional error
  100 	; EPS(2) additive error

$EST METHOD=COND INTER MAX = 9999 MSFO=MSF1 PRINT = 10
$COV UNCOND PRINT=E  PRECOND=1 PRECONDS=TOS  MATRIX = R

$SUBROUTINE ADVAN4 ;; advan4

  CWTKGONE = WT/81  ;; WEIGHT CENTERED ON ONE
  CWTKGZERO = WT-81 ;; WEIGHT CENTERED ON ZERO
  CAGE = AGE/60     ;; AGE CENTERED ON ONE
  CCRCL = CRCL/85.6 ;; CRCL CENTERD ON ONE
  CCOV1 = COV1-15.4 ;; COVARIATE 1 CENTERED ON ZERO
  IF(OCC.EQ.1) IOVV = ETA(6) 
  IF(OCC.EQ.2) IOVV = ETA(7) 
  IF(OCC.EQ.3) IOVV = ETA(8)

  K32=THETA(5)

  0.4  		; ETA(2) VOLUME

$SUBROUTINE ADVAN2 ;; advan2
$PK
  CWTKGONE = WT/81  ;; WEIGHT CENTERED ON ONE
  CWTKGZERO = WT-81 ;; WEIGHT CENTERED ON ZERO
  CAGE = AGE/60     ;; AGE CENTERED ON ONE
  CCRCL = CRCL/85.6 ;; CRCL CENTERD ON ONE
  CCOV1 = COV1-15.4 ;; COVARIATE 1 CENTERED ON ZERO
  IF(OCC.EQ.1) IOVV = ETA(4) 
  IF(OCC.EQ.2) IOVV = ETA(5) 
  IF(OCC.EQ.3) IOVV = ETA(6)
  TVV2=THETA(1)    *EXP(COV2*THETA(4))  *EXP(IOVV)
  V2=TVV2*EXP(ETA(2))
  IOVCL = 0
  TVCL= THETA(3)     *EXP(IOVCL)
  CL=TVCL*EXP(ETA(1))

  K=CL/V2
  ;; PK 1 compartment 
  ALAG1=THETA(5)
  D1=THETA(6)
  TVKA=THETA(2)
  KA=TVKA  *EXP(ETA(3)) 
  S2 = V2
$ERROR
  REP = IREP
  IPRED =F
  IOBS = F *EXP(EPS(1))+EPS(2)
  Y=IOBS
$THETA
  (0.001,100) 	; THETA(1) V  UNITS = L
  (0.001, 10) 	; THETA(2) KA UNITS = 1/HR
  (0.001,20)	; THETA(3) CL UNITS =  L/HR
  ;; THETA 1 compartment



  (-4,0.1) 	; THETA(4) EXPONENTIAL volume ~COV2 




  (0.001,0.1,1) 		;; THETA(5) ALAG1
  (0.001,0.1,1) ;;THETA(6) D1
$OMEGA
  0.1  		; ETA(1) CLEARANCE
  0.4  		; ETA(2) VOLUME
$OMEGA ;; 2nd OMEGA block 
  0.1		; ETA(3) ETA ON KA
  ;; D1 and lag, block
  ;; no iov ON CL
$OMEGA BLOCK(1) ; ETA(4)
  0.1 
$OMEGA BLOCK SAME ; ETA(5)
$OMEGA BLOCK SAME ; ETA(6)
$SIGMA
  0.1 	; EPS(1) proportional error
  100 	; EPS(2) additive error

$EST METHOD=COND INTER MAX = 9999 MSFO=MSF1 PRINT = 10

$SUBROUTINE ADVAN4 ;; advan4
$PK
  CWTKGONE = WT/81  ;; WEIGHT CENTERED ON ONE
  CWTKGZERO = WT-81 ;; WEIGHT CENTERED ON ZERO
  CAGE = AGE/60     ;; AGE CENTERED ON ONE
  CCRCL = CRCL/85.6 ;; CRCL CENTERD ON ONE
  CCOV1 = COV1-15.4 ;; COVARIATE 1 CENTERED ON ZERO
  IF(OCC.EQ.1) IOVV = ETA(4) 
  IF(OCC.EQ.2) IOVV = ETA(5) 
  IF(OCC.EQ.3) IOVV = ETA(6)
  TVV2=THETA(1)   *CAGE**THETA(6) *EXP(COV2*THETA(7))  *EXP(IOVV)
  V2=TVV2*EXP(ETA(2))
  IOVCL = 0
  TVCL= THETA(3)     *EXP(IOVCL)
  CL=TVCL*EXP(ETA(1))

  K=CL/V2
  K23=THETA(4)
  K32=THETA(5)
  ALAG1=THETA(8)
  ;; No D1
  TVKA=THETA(2)
  KA=TVKA  *EXP(ETA(3)) 
  S2 = V2
$ERROR
  REP = IREP
  IPRED =F
  IOBS = F *EXP(EPS(1))+EPS(2)
  Y=IOBS
$THETA
  (0.001,100) 	; THETA(1) V  UNITS = L
  (0.001, 10) 	; THETA(2) KA UNITS = 1/HR
  (0.001,2)	; THETA(3) CL UNITS =  L/HR
  (0.001,0.02)  	 ; THETA(4) K23 
  (0.001,0.3) 	 ; THETA(5) K32 
  ; init for K23~WT 


  (-4,0.8) 	; THETA(6) POWER volume ~AGE 
  (-4,0.1) 	; THETA(7) EXPONENTIAL volume ~COV2 




  (0.001,0.1) 	; THETA(8) ALAG1   
$OMEGA
  0.1  		; ETA(1) CLEARANCE
  0.4  		; ETA(2) VOLUME
$OMEGA ;; 2nd OMEGA block 
  0.1		; ETA(3) ETA ON KA

  ;; no iov ON CL
$OMEGA BLOCK(1) ; ETA(4)
  0.1 
$OMEGA BLOCK SAME ; ETA(5)
$OMEGA BLOCK SAME ; ETA(6)
$SIGMA
  0.1 	; EPS(1) proportional error
  100 	; EPS(2) additive error

$EST METHOD=COND INTER MAX = 9999 MSFO=MSF1 PRINT = 10
$COV UNCOND PRINT=E  PRECOND=1 PRECONDS=TOS  MATRIX = R

$SUBROUTINE ADVAN4 ;; advan4
$PK
  CWTKGONE = WT/81  ;; WEIGHT CENTERED ON ONE
  CWTKGZERO = WT-81 ;; WEIGHT CENTERED ON ZERO
  CAGE = AGE/60     ;; AGE CENTERED ON ONE
  CCRCL = CRCL/85.6 ;; CRCL CENTERD ON ONE
  CCOV1 = COV1-15.4 ;; COVARIATE 1 CENTERED ON ZERO
  IF(OCC.EQ.1) IOVV = ETA(4) 
  IF(OCC.EQ.2) IOVV = ETA(5) 
  IF(OCC.EQ.3) IOVV = ETA(6)
  TVV2=THETA(1)  *EXP(SEX*THETA(6))    *EXP(IOVV)
  V2=TVV2*EXP(ETA(2))
  IOVCL = 0
  TVCL= THETA(3)     *EXP(IOVCL)
  CL=TVCL*EXP(ETA(1))

  K=CL/V2
  K23=THETA(4)
  K32=THETA(5)
  ALAG1=THETA(7)
  ;; No D1
  TVKA=THETA(2)
  KA=TVKA  *EXP(ETA(3)) 
  S2 = V2
$ERROR
  REP = IREP
  IPRED =F
  IOBS = F *EXP(EPS(1))+EPS(2)
  Y=IOBS
$THETA
  (0.001,100) 	; THETA(1) V  UNITS = L
  (0.001, 10) 	; THETA(2) KA UNITS = 1/HR
  (0.001,20)	; THETA(3) CL UNITS =  L/HR
  (0.001,0.02)  	 ; THETA(4) K23 
  (0.001,0.3) 	 ; THETA(5) K32 
  ; init for K23~WT 

  (-4,0.1) 	; THETA(6) EXPONENTIAL volume~SEX 






  (0.001,0.1) 	; THETA(7) ALAG1   
$OMEGA
  0.1  		; ETA(1) CLEARANCE
  0.4  		; ETA(2) VOLUME
$OMEGA ;; 2nd OMEGA block 
  0.1		; ETA(3) ETA ON KA

  ;; no iov ON CL
$OMEGA BLOCK(1) ; ETA(4)
  0.1 
$OMEGA BLOCK SAME ; ETA(5)
$OMEGA BLOCK SAME ; ETA(6)
$SIGMA
  0.1 	; EPS(1) proportional error
  100 	; EPS(2) additive error

$EST METHOD=COND INTER MAX = 9999 MSFO=MSF1 PRINT = 10
$COV UNCOND PRINT=E  PRECOND=1 PRECONDS=TOS  MATRIX = R

  CWTKGZERO = WT-81 ;; WEIGHT CENTERED ON ZERO
  CAGE = AGE/60     ;; AGE CENTERED ON ONE
  CCRCL = CRCL/85.6 ;; CRCL CENTERD ON ONE
  CCOV1 = COV1-15.4 ;; COVARIATE 1 CENTERED ON ZERO
  IOVV = 0
  TVV2=THETA(1)    *EXP(COV2*THETA(6))  *EXP(IOVV)
  V2=TVV2*EXP(ETA(2))
  IOVCL = 0
  TVCL= THETA(3)     *EXP(IOVCL)
  CL=TVCL*EXP(ETA(1))

  K23=THETA(4)
  K32=THETA(5)
  ALAG1=THETA(7)*EXP(ETA(4))
  ;; No D1
  TVKA=THETA(2)
  KA=TVKA  *EXP(ETA(3)) 
  S2 = V2
$ERROR
  REP = IREP
  IPRED =F
  IOBS = F *EXP(EPS(1))+EPS(2)
  Y=IOBS
$THETA
  (0.001,100) 	; THETA(1) V  UNITS = L
  (0.001, 10) 	; THETA(2) KA UNITS = 1/HR
  (0.001,20)	; THETA(3) CL UNITS =  L/HR
  (0.001,0.02)  	 ; THETA(4) K23

  (-4,0.1) 	; THETA(6) EXPONENTIAL volume ~COV2 




  (0.001,0.1) 	; THETA(7) ALAG1

  0.1  		; ETA(1) CLEARANCE
  0.4  		; ETA(2) VOLUME

  ;; no iov ON CL

  0.1 	; EPS(1) proportional error
  100 	; EPS(2) additive error

  TVV2=THETA(1) *CWTKGONE**THETA(6) *EXP(SEX*THETA(7)) *CAGE**THETA(8)   *EXP(IOVV)

  (0.001,0.1) 	; THETA(10) ALAG1

  0.1  		; ETA(1) CLEARANCE
  0.4  		; ETA(2) VOLUME

  0.1 	; EPS(1) proportional error
  100 	; EPS(2) additive error

  CCRCL = CRCL/85.6 ;; CRCL CENTERD ON ONE

  TVV2=THETA(1)    *EXP(COV2*THETA(6))  *EXP(IOVV)

$PROBLEM    2 compartment fitting
$INPUT       ID TIME AMT DROP DV MDV EVID WT AGE SEX BUN SCR OCC CRCL COV1 COV2

$DATA      /home/CertaraUser/Desktop/FDA-OGD-ML/examples/user/Example5/dataWithPeriod.csv IGNORE=@

$SUBROUTINE ADVAN4 ;; advan4
$PK
  CWTKGONE = WT/81  ;; WEIGHT CENTERED ON ONE
  CWTKGZERO = WT-81 ;; WEIGHT CENTERED ON ZERO
  CAGE = AGE/60     ;; AGE CENTERED ON ONE
  CCRCL = CRCL/85.6 ;; CRCL CENTERD ON ONE
  CCOV1 = COV1-15.4 ;; COVARIATE 1 CENTERED ON ZERO
  IF(OCC.EQ.1) IOVV = ETA(4) 
  IF(OCC.EQ.2) IOVV = ETA(5) 
  IF(OCC.EQ.3) IOVV = ETA(6)
  TVV2=THETA(1)   *CAGE**THETA(7) *EXP(COV2*THETA(8))  *EXP(IOVV)
  V2=TVV2*EXP(ETA(2))
  IOVCL = 0
  TVCL= THETA(3)    *EXP(CCOV1*THETA(9)) *EXP(IOVCL)
  CL=TVCL*EXP(ETA(1))

  K=CL/V2
  K23=THETA(4)*CWTKGONE**THETA(6)
  K32=THETA(5)*CWTKGONE**THETA(6)
  ALAG1=THETA(10)
  ;; No D1
  TVKA=THETA(2)
  KA=TVKA  *EXP(ETA(3)) 
  S2 = V2
$ERROR
  REP = IREP
  IPRED =F
  IOBS = F +EPS(1)
  Y=IOBS
$THETA
  (0.001,100) 	; THETA(1) V  UNITS = L
  (0.001, 10) 	; THETA(2) KA UNITS = 1/HR
  (0.001,2)	; THETA(3) CL UNITS =  L/HR
  (0.001,0.02)  	 ; THETA(4) K23 
  (0.001,0.3) 	 ; THETA(5) K32 
  (0,0.1) 	; THETA(6) K23~WT 	 ; init for K23~WT 


  (-4,0.8) 	; THETA(7) POWER volume ~AGE 
  (-4,0.1) 	; THETA(8) EXPONENTIAL volume ~COV2 



  (-4,0.1) 	; THETA(9) EXPONENTIAL CL~COV1 
  (0.001,0.1) 	; THETA(10) ALAG1   
$OMEGA
  0.1  		; ETA(1) CLEARANCE
  0.4  		; ETA(2) VOLUME
$OMEGA ;; 2nd OMEGA block 
  0.1		; ETA(3) ETA ON KA

  ;; no iov ON CL
$OMEGA BLOCK(1) ; ETA(4)
  0.1 
$OMEGA BLOCK SAME ; ETA(5)
$OMEGA BLOCK SAME ; ETA(6)
$SIGMA
  200 	; EPS(1) additive error

$EST METHOD=COND INTER MAX = 9999 MSFO=MSF1 PRINT = 10
$COV UNCOND PRINT=E  PRECOND=1 PRECONDS=TOS  MATRIX = R
